        <h2 class="feature-num" style="opacity: 1; transform: translate(0px, 0px);"><span class="number">3</span> <span class="feature-text label">cities</span></h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="bootcamp-intro-cards">
      <div class="bootcamp-intro-card">
        <p class="left bootcamp-text">Have you always been dreaming of studying Chinese?<br>Have you started already and are struggling?<br>Have you started many times but never got anywhere?</p>
        <%= image_tag "study.svg", class: "bootcamp-img", size: "200" %>
      </div>
      <div class="bootcamp-intro-card">
        <%= image_tag "guide.svg", class: "bootcamp-img", size: "200" %>
        <p class="right bootcamp-text">If so, then this bootcamp is for you. It will guide you to fluency in <strong>six months</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bootcamp-intro-card">
        <p class="left bootcamp-text">This Chinese learning bootcamp has been designed to help students develop <strong>self-efficacy</strong> so they can make <strong>real progress</strong> and feel <strong>empowered</strong> to carry on.</p>
        <%= image_tag "fly.svg", class: "bootcamp-img", size: "200" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sect sect--padding-bottom">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
