                <div class="item__avatar avatar__one"></div>
                <p class="item__people">David Holmes</p>
                <p class="item__occupation">London Alumni</p>
              </div>

              <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="item__content">
                  <img class="item__img" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dab0abars/image/upload/v1647365725/FluentChinese_Logo_Red_kilm7y.svg" alt="FluentChinese"><span class="item__name"></span>
                  <p class="item__description">It has been a great experience to study courses with teachers in a small group. They proved to be engaging and entertaining teachers, providing us with interesting and challenging exercises every time. I was also very satisfied with the course layout. It’s well structured and well paced.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="item__avatar avatar__two"></div>
                <p class="item__people">Cecilia Tompson</p>
                <p class="item__occupation">Amsterdam Alumni</a>
              </div>

              <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="item__content">
                  <img class="item__img" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dab0abars/image/upload/v1647365725/FluentChinese_Logo_Red_kilm7y.svg" alt="FluentChinese"><span class="item__name"></span>
                  <p class="item__description">Classes are very interactive. Topics are very interesting. Teachers will share some wordings used by local people in China. Lots of practice opportunities in day-to-day conversations. Practice with specific topics, care of individual needs just in case.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="item__avatar avatar__three"></div>
                <p class="item__people">Alice Palmer</p>
                <p class="item__occupation">Australia Alumni</a>
              </div>

            </div>

            <!-- Left and right controls -->
            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">
